Male holotype (51–52, 55–56) and female paratype (53-54, 57). 51–54. Chelicera, retro-lateral view (51, 53), pro-lateral view (52, 54). 55. Tibia and tarsus, retro-lateral view. 56–57. Pedipalp retro-lateral view. Scales: 51–55: 0.3 mm, 56–57.
